title: {BigFish}Magic Match-The Genies Journey
description:
No Need For Patches Or Serials Just Run Installer And Enjoy The Game!

The hit game Magic Match returns, and Giggles the lovable Imp is now a Genie! Go on a quest with Merlin and Giggles as they seek to change Giggles back to his impish self. Cross through the desert lands of Arcania to outwit a master thief, explore the pyramids, and traverse the City of Gods in this magical and mesmerizing puzzle adventure. 
3 gameplay modes. 
5 bonus games. 
Collectible ranks and rewards.

System Requirements:

OS: Windows 2000/XP/VISTA 
CPU: 600MHz or faster Processor 
RAM: 128 MB
